high_descs: Turn and go to the counter by the microwave.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn and go to the sink.
Cut the apple in the sink.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn left and go to the sink.
Pick up a slice of apple in the sink.
Turn and go to the microwave.
Heat the slice of apple in the microwave.
Turn and go to the sink.
Put the slice of apple in the sink.
